{"tid":2402828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文願「講粵語的朋友抱持信念、不要放棄」 用廣東話祝福「新年平安」","createTime":"2021-02-10T16:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T18:10:37.000Z","uid":63183,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bbe9dc6a7ead94fb646635c2be7afcde43c5bb","tid":2402828,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GXVt3i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GXVt3i.png&h=53c2d707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSOURCE:<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5170&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=b337d5ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5170</a><br />\n今晚（10號）係年廿九，台灣總統蔡英文一如以往拍片祝福台灣市民同全球華人，其中特別提到「講粵語的朋友」，佢請大家抱持信念，不要放棄，並用廣東話同大家講「新年平安」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lBIWRw00nHw&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlBIWRw00nHw%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=49f87375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lBIWRw00nHw&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n佢全段話係咁講：「有許多講粵語的朋友，過去一年，謝謝大家繼續關注我的臉書，我也請你們相信，民主制度也許不完美，但依然是目前為止人類社會最好的制度。請大家抱持信念，不要放棄，也跟大家說一聲，『（廣東話）新年平安』。」<br />\n<br />\n自蔡英文上任以來，台灣更加重視除咗國語以外嘅其他各種中文，所以蔡英文都有用客家話講：「客家鄉親，新年恭喜，四海大平安」。<br />\n<br />\n佢又提到疫情，話隨住全球疫苗施打率逐漸提高，希望唔只台灣生活如常，全世界都可以恢復正常。台灣都會透過外購同國內研發取得疫苗，等國內民眾依序獲得疫苗嘅保護。希望牛年來到後，「就讓我們一起扭轉疫情、牛轉乾坤，經濟更繁榮、景氣更暢旺！」"},{"pid":"3d3cf837bbc024e37f43338787df7d82ce680c8f","tid":2402828,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a436854b539c23d07fe3aaa23011709c78477f09","tid":2402828,"uid":13173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"Connect 埋本土同海外廣東人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5759ace55dd19a8170be5562969bdca0c216ee1","tid":2402828,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"同維尼個拜年比高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}